  "text": "Inconsistent behavior in `h` when there is only one non-string, non-number variadic child.\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.0-beta.8\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://codesandbox.io/s/relaxed-kare-kmkgb?file=/src/App.vue](https://codesandbox.io/s/relaxed-kare-kmkgb?file=/src/App.vue)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18677354/128740344-32988136-0bc8-4e50-9568-76a2287024b6.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nfollow the link\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nshow nothing\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nshow `false`\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
